*tomcat-5.5.20 (28 Sep 2006)

  28 Sep 2006; William L. Thomson Jr. <wltjr@gentoo.org>
  +files/5.5.20/catalinabuild-xml.patch,
  +files/5.5.20/jasperbuild-xml.patch,
  +files/5.5.20/jsr152build-xml-examples.patch,
